reviewText: WOW!  This is such an awesome and powerful ministry tool to bring about deliverance.  Are you ready to break chains, loosen bondage and pull down strongholds by putting your Armor of God on?  Also includes a great workout involving punching and kicking.
Being a dancers means also to fight against the enemy through the prayer, the fasting AND the dance. Here pastor Lynn teaches you to be a weapon with powerful movements.
This is a powerful DVD!  Equipping dancers for spiritual battle.  It is also a great cardio workout!  I absolutely loved it!!!!!!!!!!!!

This is a mighty video that should not be taken for granted.  Through our movements of warfare, we are able to worship God and slay devils in our lives and the lives of others. Who are we?  We are conquerors!

I really enjoyed doing the punching and kicking of breakthrough. You will learn a lot of different movements for warfare. It is breathe taking how powerful we can be through our movements because He lives in us!

This is a way to declare our victory and triumph over the enemy through power movements! Pastor Lynn explains some Hebrew words and Scriptures that depict movement and she demonstrates those for us in an engaging way. Fun workout too! (To get the most benefit I highly recommend also getting her book "Dance, Dance, Dance.")

This DVD is full of ideas for guarding ourselves against Satan's attacks with different kinds of warfare movements.  Great to use in your private intercessory prayer times and also with groups.  I highly recommend Pastor Lynn's Dance, Dance, Dance book and her "Having Done All" CD to use with this amazing DVD.
This a great DVD to learn how to use body movement in your prayer and intercession time.  Pastor teaches breakthrough movements that relate to scriptures.  You will also enjoy a good workout.
